units metal
boundary p p p
atom_style atomic

# ── Crystal Setup ──
lattice bcc 3.0299999301794
Lattice spacing in x,y,z = 3.0299999 3.0299999 3.0299999
region box block 0 5 0 5 0 5
create_box 1 box
